INSERT INTO "fio_juvenile" VALUES ('FC25001788','2025-04-22 13:50','126514','SCHAIN, RYAN','KEVIN MCCLAY','CENTRE ST','JAMAICA PLAIN','MA','02130','NULL','Stopped','Probable Cause','NULL','NULL','OTHER: RED',NULL,'Red',NULL,'Moped',NULL,'Juvenile','YVSF intel - VK23  Officers observed a red moped occupied by two young males drive out of the Heath Street housing development onto Centre Street. Officers noted the rear passenger did not have a helmet on, and further noted the moped did not have a license plate or registration sticker. Officers observed the moped pull up to Evelyn''s Market at XXXCentre and observed the operator exit the moped and go inside. Once the driver was off the moped, Officers successfully stopped it without incident. The operator was identified as XXX (open firearm case), and the passenger was identified as XXX (open firearm case). Both males have previous incidents withXXX, who is currently wanted for a shooting incident on B2.   XXXand XXXwere wearing heavy winter coats, despite a 70+ degree air temperature. Given the fact that recent gun violence within and coming out of the Heath Street development has been done by young males on scooters, the fact that both males were overdressed for the weather, along with their open firearm cases and associations with a male wanted for a recent shooting, both were frisked for weapons with negative results.  A check of the moped''s VIN # XXXrevealed it was not reported stolen. Both XXXand XXXwere FIO''d and released.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-04-22','13:50',2025,4,22);
