INSERT INTO "fio_juvenile" VALUES ('FC25003830','2025-07-19 21:18','116141','DEVITO, AMYLEIGH','JOHN HUGHES','NULL','DORCHESTER','MA','02121','NULL','Stopped','Reasonable Suspicion','NULL','MA','Focus',NULL,'Gray','4 Door, Sedan','Passenger Car/ Automobile',NULL,'Juvenile, Body Worn Camera, Other Agency/Unit Notified','About 2118 hours on Saturday, July 19th, 2025, Sgt. Det. DeVito (B982) responded to Georgia Street and Blue Hill Avenue to assist MSP who requested assistance with a traffic stop. Upon arrival a Trooper said they would be removing someone from the car and there were four occupants. They tried to remove the right side rear passenger and had to reach through an open window to open the door and then the passenger was hesitant to get out. The male had a light brown complexion (unknown race/ethnicity), braids, and was wearing a baggy, light gray "Sp5der" hoodie, blue jeans, and white and black sneakers.  While they were removing him, S/D DeVito observed the female front passenger had her hands tightly clasped at the bottom of her hoodie and appeared to be pushing down the bottom of her hoodie, while their chest was visibly rising and falling.   XXXDOB: XX/XX/XXXXwas removed and frisked by S/D DeVito. Nothing was located. She was observed to be visibly sweating and breathing heavily. She said she was hot, then also said she had no bra on, which was why she was wearing a hoodie. She also said her boyfriend wanted her covered up while with other males. She said they were doing Door Dash deliveries. She said the driver was her boyfriend.   The driver was a heavy set male wearing a red zipper hoodie, black shorts, white socks, and red Crocs. He had a light brown complexion and long hair in a ponytail. The vehicle, a gray Ford Focus XXXwas registered to XXXDOB: XX/XX/XXXXwhich resembled the driver.  MSP concluded their stop and released all the parties.  A female and male arrived on scene and took the rear driver''s side passenger, who they identified as their 1