INSERT INTO "fio_juvenile" VALUES ('FC25004650','2025-08-27 06:40','173547','Kelley, Johnpaul','JAMES MOORE','NULL','BOSTON','MA','02121','NULL','Stopped','Reasonable Suspicion','NULL','NULL','NULL',NULL,'NULL','NULL','NULL',NULL,'Car Jack, Juvenile, Body Worn Camera','About 6:40 AM on Wednesday, 08/27/2025, Officers Kelley and Colon in the B201A conducted a subject stop in relation to a carjacking at Sonoma St and Maple St, Dorchester.  Officers were patrolling the area of Elm Hill Ave and Hutchings Street due to the victim stating her car was pinging in the area. Prior to this information, Officer Barros (B611A), notified operations that he had observed the motor vehicle, a white Chevy Malibu (FL REG XXXoccupied twice at the intersection of Crawford St and Waumbeck St. Officer Barros stated that once the occupants in the vehicle observed him, they took off going the wrong way down Waumbeck St. Officers began canvassing the area and located the vehicle unoccupied in a parking lot at XXXHutchings St along with multiple other units. Officer Barros stated that he observed a black male in the driver seat lying down with his foot on the steering wheel. Officer Barros stated the driver was wearing a gray hooded sweatshirt and black Adidas pants.  Officers began patrolling the area and observed a male matching the exact description given by Officer Barros at the intersection of Sonoma St and Maple St. Officer Kelley and Colon exited their cruiser and frisked the male due to a silver handgun being used in the carjacking. Officers identified the male as XXX (DOB XX/XX/XXXXOfficer Barros responded to the scene and confirmed that this was the male who he had saw in the driver''s seat. Officers briefly detained the male and was FIOD and released.  It should be noted thatXXXwas confrontational towards officers and was visibly sweating.XXXstated to officers that he was walking from the area of Elm Hill Ave going to his sister''s residence at Nazing Ct.  Officers were unable to conduct a CJIS Inquiry onXXXdue to CJIS being down.  BWC Activated.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2025-08-27','06:40',2025,8,27);
